Text: San Diego Gas and ElectricThe meeting is at pm today Aaron if you come to my office we will walk over to Saras office and have the meeting there I have spoken to Francisco and got a good data dump from him there is no need for him to join us this afternoon I have the traders name we should call him during our meeting In order to move forward we need three things The PwC valuation of the financial contracts A better understanding of the physical contracts and what happened A good data dump from the trader Once we have this information we should approach SDGE Lets aim at having first contact tomorrow morning

RE Will you be in the office on Friday Id like to catch up SaraAbsolutely when do you want to meet Original Message From Shackleton Sara Sent Thursday February PM To Baumfield Richard Subject Will you be in the office on Friday Id like to catch up Sara Sara Shackleton Enron Wholesale Services Smith Street EBa Houston TX Ph Fax
